title: Python Developer - Entry Level
description:
We're looking for an entry-level Python Developer to help build our web application.

Key Responsibilities:
- Write Python code for our Django web application
- Fix bugs and add small features
- Learn from senior developers
- Participate in code reviews

Required Skills:
- 0-1 years of Python experience (recent grads welcome!)
- Basic knowledge of Django or Flask
- Familiarity with HTML/CSS/JavaScript
- Willingness to learn

Preferred Skills:
- Internship experience
- Portfolio of personal projects
- Computer Science degree

Our Tech Stack:
- Backend: Python 3.9, Django
- Frontend: React, TypeScript
- Database: PostgreSQL
- Hosting: Heroku

We're a small startup (10 people) building a SaaS product for small businesses. This is a great opportunity to learn and grow your skills in a supportive environment.

Note: This is an entry-level position with mentorship and growth opportunities. We're not expecting extensive experience, just eagerness to learn!
company_info: StartupCo is a 10-person startup building project management software for small businesses. We're pre-Series A and focused on finding product-market fit.
skip_reason: Score below threshold (lacks senior-level experience and requirements)
